2014-01-21  Hristian Kirtchev  <kirtchev@adacore.com>

	* sem_ch3.adb (Analyze_Variable_Contract): Trigger the volatile
	object check when SPARK_Mode is on.
	* sem_ch6.adb (Process_Formals): Trigger the volatile object
